text: Tabatha “dream”Robinson (stage name: DreamDoll; born February 28, 1992), is an American rapper from the Bronx. She came out as bisexual and was on Billboard charts including her song "Ah Ah Ah". She was put onto Warner Records. == Personal life == In January 2, 2025, Dreamdoll announced that she is pregnant with her first child. In March, 2025, Dreamdoll gave birth to a daughter. == References == Category:1992 births Category:Rappers from New York (state) Category:Living people Category:Musicians from the Bronx
